OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA few morning showers with
OL,6,Fsunny spells, but the afternoon looks
OL,7,Fdry with some longer spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine. Northwesterly breeze,
OL,9,Foccasionally strong near coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,12,Fwith sunny spells Saturday, some
OL,13,Fevening rain. Overnight rain soon
OL,14,Fclearing Sunday then sunny spells and
OL,15,Fa few showers. Rather cloudy Monday
OL,16,Fwith a little rain. Becoming milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
